<http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/pizza.owl#InterestingPizza> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Any pizza that has at least 3 toppings. Note that this is a cardinality constraint on the hasTopping property and NOT a qualified cardinality constraint (QCR). A QCR would specify from which class the members in this relationship must be. eg has at least 3 toppings from PizzaTopping. This is currently not supported in OWL." .
